cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.DS 

The paper deals with proving the validity of replica predictions for mutual information in Bayesian inference problems. This involves techniques from information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), statistical inference (cs.SI), and data structures (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
